      <mj-column padding="0px 15px">
        <mj-text color="#ffffff" font-size="24px" font-weight="bold" font-style="italic" padding-top="70px">We would like to invite you to the opening of Dell's DXR Studios in Singapore. </mj-text>
        <mj-text color="#ffffff" padding-bottom="70px">Come and meet the team at DXR Studios from Dell - the holistic, full-service provider making enterprise-grade AR, VR, XR reality today. </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-color="#000000">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image width="350px" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fayeli/email-templates/main/assets/martin-headshot.png" />
        <mj-text color="#fff">
        As XR designers, engineers, consultants, & evangelists, we believe in the transformative potential of XR - at scale and driving real value.		
      	</mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-color="#000000">
      <mj-column padding="0px 15px">
        <mj-text color="#ffffff" font-size="24px" font-weight="bold" font-style="italic" padding-top="70px">You're personally invited. </mj-text>
        <mj-text color="#ffffff">This is your personal invite to explore the DXR Studios space in Singapore, and to meet the head of DXR, Martin Sawtell for a 1:1 discussion on your clients and where XR could help. </mj-text>
        <mj-text color="#ffffff">Click below to book your intro chat now </mj-text>
        <mj-button href="https://www.calendly.com" padding-top="45px" background-color="#1B54DD"> Book a Session </mj-button>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-color="#000000" padding-top="50px" padding-bottom="20px">
